= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Experience Table =

This page documents the experience point requirements for all playable characters in '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version).

== Overview ==

Unlike previous Dragon Warrior games, Dragon Warrior IV features unique experience tables for each character. This reflects their different starting levels and progression rates across the five chapters.

Experience values are stored as 3-byte (24-bit) values allowing a maximum of 16,777,215 EXP. Level cap is 99 for all characters.

